@c-------------------------------------------------------------------------
@node REQUIREMENTS "Requirements"

To run zmime, you need Kickstart 2.1 or better and @{"MUI" link ABOUT_MUI} Release 3.1 or
better. To make full use of all features, you also need a @{"text editor" link EDITOR}
and a @{"sendmail agent" link SENDING_MSGS}. The builtin language is english. If you want to use
catalog files (currently there's only a german catalog), locale.library is
also required.

@endnode
